{"tid":1238291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位加油","createTime":"2019-06-17T18:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T15:32:40.000Z","uid":148279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c932d01cf4436372465c5ec511d8f1b277b66a00","tid":1238291,"uid":148279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:18:19.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好因為一時嘅成功而沖昏頭腦<br />\n而家我地就好似清理渠口<br />\n塞左，點知一拉起，啲頭髮，鳩毛，纏到一舊舊<br />\n我地唔可以唔理<br />\n就等同而家香港<br />\n一層一層掀起<br />\n越掀越多<br />\n警察，醫管局，林奠<br />\n今次我地一定要對抗<br />\n因為我地而家唔企起黎，可能再冇機會。<br />\n以下係俾嗰啲冇參與嘅人<br />\n唔好等到冇人企出黎先行動<br />\n亦都唔洗覺得企出黎要有好多理由<br />\n最簡單直接嘅理由就係因為香港係自己屋企<br />\n<br />\n<strong>各位加油</strong>"},{"pid":"807f7eeb861a497b2c92609f4d6649b695182e43","tid":1238291,"uid":192893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T18:18:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/34T-zGLUL8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F34T-zGLUL8Q&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=2c730819\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/34T-zGLUL8Q</a>"},{"pid":"2789e60c5ebf466aa63802af6c9658d5c54fb11e","tid":1238291,"uid":148279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}